summary: This is an automated email notification from the E2 Solutions travel system informing a recipient that a final travel voucher (ID 11062816(1)) is pending their review. The voucher is for official travel related to the 'Epstein Investigation - Witness interview' that occurred from February 19-20, 2020, with total expenses of $1,040.52.

events.title: Epstein Investigation Witness Interview Travel
events.description: Official travel was conducted for the purpose of a witness interview related to the Epstein investigation.

keyFacts: The document is a travel voucher notification related to the Epstein investigation, indicating ongoing investigative activity as of February 2020.
The travel purpose is explicitly stated as 'R20NYS13401 - Epstein Investigation - Witness interview'.
The travel occurred from February 19 to February 20, 2020, with total expenses of $1,040.52.
The document originates from the U.S. Department of Justice's E2 Solutions travel system, indicating this is official government business.
The voucher status was 'Pending Voucher Approval' as of February 24, 2020.
